<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Algorithm code="             1. Let _lNum_ be ! ToUint32(_x_).             1. Let _rNum_ be ! ToUint32(_y_).             1. Let _shiftCount_ be ℝ(_rNum_) modulo 32.             1. Return the result of performing a zero-filling right shift of _lNum_ by _shiftCount_ bits. Vacated bits are filled with zero. The mathematical value of the result is exactly representable as a 32-bit unsigned bit string.           ">
